#. Tag: para
#: libvirt_storage.xml:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Provide a <guimenu>Name</guimenu> for the pool (consisting of alphanumeric characters and <literal>_-.</literal> ) and select a <guimenu>Type</guimenu> . Proceed with <guimenu>Forward</guimenu> ."
